
<h2>Receipt</h2>

<p>Thank you for your order from the Foreign & Commonwealth Office. We have taken payment for the following:</p>

<div class ="content-block">
	<div class ="application-notice info-notice">
		<p>Date: <%= date %></p>
		<p>Payment Reference: <%= responseParameters.merchantReference %></p>
		<p>Service: <%= transaction.slug %></p>
		<p>Amount: &pound;<%= formatMoney(responseParameters.paymentAmount) %></p>
		<p>You have paid for <%= pluralise("death registration", registrationCount(merchantReturnDataJson)) %> and <%= pluralise("certificate", documentCount(merchantReturnDataJson)) %> and postage coverage to <%=capitalise(merchantReturnDataJson.po) %>.</p>
	</div>
</div>
